  "prompt": "How do I change One Plus 3 ringtone?",
  "response": "Changing the ringtone on your OnePlus 3 is a straightforward process. Here\u2019s how you can do it:\n\n### Method 1: Using Settings\n1. **Open Settings:**\n   - Swipe down from the top of the screen to access the notification shade and tap on the **gear icon** to open the Settings app.\n\n2. **Go to Sound Settings:**\n   - Scroll down and tap on **Sound & vibration**.\n\n3. **Select Ringtone:**\n   - Tap on **Phone ringtone**.\n\n4. **Choose a Ringtone:**\n   - You will see a list of available ringtones. Tap on the one you want to use.\n\n5. **Set the Ringtone:**\n   - Once you\u2019ve selected your desired ringtone, tap **OK** or **Set** to apply it.\n\n### Method 2: Using a File Manager\nIf you want to use a custom ringtone that you\u2019ve downloaded or created, you can set it using a file manager.\n\n1. **Place the Ringtone File:**\n   - Move your custom ringtone file to the **Ringtones** folder on your OnePlus 3. You can use a file manager app like **Files by Google** or **ES File Explorer** to do this.\n\n2. **Open Settings:**\n   - Go to **Settings** > **Sound & vibration**.\n\n3. **Select Ringtone:**\n   - Tap on **Phone ringtone**.\n\n4. **Choose Your Custom Ringtone:**\n   - Scroll through the list to find your custom ringtone. It should appear in the list if you placed it in the correct folder.\n\n5. **Set the Ringtone:**\n   - Tap on your custom ringtone and then **OK** or **Set** to apply it.\n\n### Method 3: Using Contacts App\nYou can also set a specific ringtone for a particular contact.\n\n1. **Open Contacts:**\n   - Open the **Contacts** app on your OnePlus 3.\n\n2. **Select a Contact:**\n   - Tap on the contact for whom you want to set a custom ringtone.\n\n3. **Edit Contact:**\n   - Tap on the **Edit** icon (usually a pencil or edit symbol).\n\n4. **Set Ringtone:**\n   - Scroll down and tap on **Ringtone**.\n\n5. **Choose a Ringtone:**\n   - Select the ringtone you want to use for this contact.\n\n6. **Save Changes:**\n   - Tap **Save** or **Done** to apply the changes.\n\nThat\u2019s it! You\u2019ve successfully changed the ringtone on your OnePlus 3.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
